    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that operates without noise or hesitation. The power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with structural plates and has had the rod bearing service completed to factory specifications. The suspension geometry remains true, with refreshed bushings and original dampers providing a taut, communicative ride. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with a deep, swirl-free luster, the exterior is complemented by a flawless Cinnamon Nappa leather interior. No mechanical compromises, no codes, and a clean underside.",
